    • Field Detail

      • ORDERED_MEMBER_LIST

        public static final java.lang.Object[] ORDERED_MEMBER_LIST
        this constant list causes the members to come out in specified order. this allows the name, parameters, and description to be seen at the top of the profile. NodeType must be present in list for JSON source to be recognized as a profile. Description is also forced out as NULL if otherwise not present. this all makes the profile a consistent document format.
